1. DEFINITIONS

   "Software" refers to the Memorize source code, documentation, and any
   associated materials in this repository.

   "Derivative Work" means any modification, enhancement, bug fix, or feature
   addition to the Software.

   "Cache Service Business" means a business that sells caching, key-value
   storage, or similar data storage services as its primary product offering,
   comparable to Redis Cloud, Amazon ElastiCache, Azure Cache, or similar.

   "Internal Use" means use of the Software within your organization or as
   a component of your applications, where caching is not the product being sold.

2. GRANT OF RIGHTS

   Subject to the terms of this License, you are granted a perpetual,
